snippet.title: No Respite from Queues in Several Cities after Introduction of Ink System

localized.description:
No respite from queue in several cities after introduction of ink system. There is a drop in queue outside ATMs and banks after RBI introduces indelible ink to stop multiple transactions. Peoples were struggling to exchange and deposit currency notes of Rs 500 and Rs 1000 after Modi government demonetisation decision.
